libbbs
------------------------------------------
telnet Bulletin Board System (BBS) helper library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libbbs-devel-0.0.0+git20140813-1bl2
  libbbs0-0.0.0+git20140813-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pcman-bbs/libbbs

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pcman-bbs/libbbs.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libbbs-0.0.0+git20140813-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libbbs-0.0.0+git20140813-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libbbs-0.0.0+git20140813-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbbs-0.0.0+git20140813-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbbs0-0.0.0+git20140813-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbbs-devel-0.0.0+git20140813-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libbbs)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libbbs.README
  /usr/share/doc/libbbs/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libbbs/README.md

(libbbs0)
  /usr/bin/cygbbs-0.dll

(libbbs-devel)
  /usr/include/bbs/bbs.h
  /usr/lib/libbbs.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/bbs.pc

------------------

